* Previous Releases
	
	Earlier versions of NEsper can be downloaded from {{{http://dist.codehaus.org/esper}here}}.


* Prerequisite For Clients 

	.NET Framework minimum of 3.5 


* Installation Steps 

	Installation from distributed MSI 
		
	* Run the MSI 

	* Select components 

	* Select installation directory (defaults to [Program Files]\Espertech\Esper) 
	
	[]
	
	
	Installation from Zip File 
	
	* Select installation directory 

	* Unzip contents into installation directory 

* Server

	* This is a CEP component for inclusion into your own application process and does not include a server executable to run.